{"tid":1539822,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"五大訴求 缺一不可！ 另外可以再加兩個","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:11:21.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"733b4f328cb44c75b1398e46ec249bf04b05040b","tid":1539822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"一）徹底撤回修例<br />\n二）收回暴動定義<br />\n三）撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四）解散警隊，徹底追究警隊濫權情況，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五）以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n其他訴求<br />\n<br />\n六）清拆所有監控燈柱，並承諾不再興建任何監控設施<br />\n七)  追究港鐵相關責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要記得下面活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n907和你塞3.0<br />\n908美國領事館"},{"pid":"9f5ecbf2a707a24e1ad5b20c24a2d95d57808140","tid":1539822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060ec6874bffa21b71b0e447203c1f6d796251a4","tid":1539822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3273605b0c60962baf4ab435804430355aeb7b","tid":1539822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfddd59dfd96ba1462668261309e7255f2f8888b","tid":1539822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da7b2416221cd54344f925e12b22e23a1101f6f","tid":1539822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src